description=WebUI-based CA certificate installer for the Android System trust store. Upload any PEM/DER/CRT/CER/P7B/P7C; subject_hash is computed in-browser. Supports Magisk/KernelSU/SukiSU/APatch. Android 5.0-15 with APEX bypass for Android 14+.
